      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，是一个经典的branch and merge场景。我理解为：从main出发，创建newbranch做特性开发，完成后checkout回main再做merge。需要显示几次commit？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
