      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，两次commit就够了——第一次在main的初始提交，第二次在newbranch上的特性提交。这样简洁清晰，适合给团队做 onboarding 材料。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "main",
        "newbranch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我开始绘制。先设置标题为Simple \"branch and merge\" (Retail_OrderManagement)，然后布局用LR横向展示。第一步：main上初始commit。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
